<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Jobs Live - Landing Page</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f4f4f9;
      color: #333;
    }
    header {
      background: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    header p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    main {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .section {
      margin: 2rem 0; 
    }
    .section h2 {
      color: #007bff;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 1rem 0;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
      background: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background: #0056b3;
    }
    .platform-links a {
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #007bff;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .social-buttons a {
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #007bff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      color: #007bff;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .social-buttons a:hover {
      background: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      background: #333;
      color: #fff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to Jobs Live</h1>
    <p>Connecting businesses and workers for fast job opportunities</p>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section class="section" id="about">
      <h2>About Jobs Live</h2>
      <p>Jobs Live is a project built for educational purposes, aimed at creating a system that connects businesses with workers, enabling quick and efficient job searches.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="register">
      <h2>Sign Up Now</h2>
      <a href="#" class="button">Register Your Account</a>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="platforms">
      <h2>Platforms</h2>
      <p class="platform-links">
        <a href="#">Web Platform</a>
        <a href="#">Mobile App (App Store)</a>
        <a href="#">Mobile App (Google Play)</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="contact">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <div class="social-buttons">
        <a href="#">Facebook</a>
        <a href="#">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Jobs Live. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>